@startuml
title Arquitectura Física y Stack Tecnológico - Jorgestor

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

node "Navegador del Usuario" as ClientNode {
    component "Frontend App\n(React + Vite)" as Frontend <<Web Interface>>
    note right of Frontend
        - TypeScript
        - TanStack Query
        - Axios
        - CSS Modules
    end note
}

node "Servidor de Aplicaciones (JVM 21)" as ServerNode {
    
    package "API REST (Spring Boot 3.2.5)" {
        component "Controladores" as API <<Controller Layer>>
        component "Servicios de Negocio" as Services <<Service Layer>>
        component "Persistencia (JPA/Hibernate)" as DataLayer <<Repository Layer>>
        
        note bottom of Services
            - Algoritmo de Generación
            - Motor de Calificación
            - Seguridad RBAC
            - Hashing SHA-256
        end note
    }
}

node "Servidor de Datos" as DBNode {
    database "PostgreSQL 17" as DB <<Database>>
    note bottom of DB
        - Esquema 3FN
        - ACID Compliant
        - Tabla 'Matriculas' (N:M)
    end note
}

' Relaciones de Interacción y Protocolos
Frontend -down-> API : HTTP / JSON (REST)
API -down-> Services : Inyección de Dependencias
Services -down-> DataLayer : Mapeo de Objetos
DataLayer -down-> DB : SQL / JDBC

center footer © 2026 Jorgestor - Ingeniería del Software II (IDSW2)
@enduml
